This is the explanation for running scripts;

On python version 3, third package required < matplotlib >



To check its help usage;

python[3] filter-1.80.py -h



Run the samples for test;

1) single inputs:
    python[3] filter-1.80.py -f long*

    OR silently, without double check:
        python[3] filter-1.80.py -f long* -nc


2) multiple inputs:
    python[3] filter-1.80.py -f data* -d index*

    OR silently, without double check:
        python[3] filter-1.80.py -f data* -d index* -nc





